						<div class="postbody">In a nutshell it looks like this?<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; PHA<br />&nbsp; STA temp<br />&nbsp; LDA temp<br />&nbsp; TXA<br />&nbsp; PHA<br />&nbsp; STA temp<br />&nbsp; LDA temp<br />&nbsp; TYA<br />&nbsp; pha<br />&nbsp; LDA temp</div></div>

					
